WEBVTT

00:19.080 --> 00:21.240
THE MASTER OF KNOWING HEARTS

00:46.440 --> 00:47.360
Being so content that one forgets home.

00:47.440 --> 00:49.520
Think this can fool me?

01:00.880 --> 01:02.320
Where is that Sui fellow taking Changning?

01:06.400 --> 01:09.080
Relax. That foolish brother of mine

01:10.640 --> 01:12.960
still thinks she's
Marquis Wu'an's daughter.

01:13.680 --> 01:15.160
He can't bear to kill her.

01:17.800 --> 01:18.880
Marquis Wu'an?

01:20.160 --> 01:21.200
What Marquis Wu'an?

01:21.960 --> 01:24.600
The mighty Marquis Wu'an could actually
marry into a pig-slaughterer's family?

01:25.120 --> 01:27.200
What could be more absurd than that?

01:29.280 --> 01:30.480
What?

01:35.280 --> 01:37.560
Are you really not understanding,
or are you pretending not to?

01:39.160 --> 01:40.800
Aren't you usually quite clever?

01:44.120 --> 01:45.040
I said,

01:45.120 --> 01:49.160
Marquis Wu'an, Xie Zheng, married into
the family of pig-slaughterer Fan Changyu.

01:53.400 --> 01:56.720
You mean Yan Zheng is Marquis Wu'an?

01:57.600 --> 02:04.560
LUCHENG MILITARY CAMP

02:10.720 --> 02:12.560
Marquis, a letter
from the Chongzhou army scouts.

02:17.000 --> 02:17.920
This Sui Yuanqing

02:18.560 --> 02:21.160
wants me to exchange Yanzhou
for Changning.

02:23.280 --> 02:26.320
This Sui Yuanqing
is getting more arrogant.

02:26.400 --> 02:27.680
Convey my military order.

02:27.760 --> 02:29.960
Have the vanguard battalion
follow me to Baxia.

02:30.680 --> 02:33.600
To bring my daughter back unharmed.

02:34.200 --> 02:35.160
Yes.

02:40.040 --> 02:41.080
Brother.

02:43.080 --> 02:43.920
Yuanqing.

02:48.240 --> 02:50.200
You came at the right time. Scouts report

02:50.280 --> 02:51.680
that scoundrel Xie Zheng
actually led troops

02:51.760 --> 02:53.520
and wiped out a whole squad
of our border guards.

02:55.800 --> 02:56.680
Excellent.

02:57.240 --> 02:59.480
At my command,
all troops prepare for battle.

03:00.080 --> 03:01.280
-Yes.
-Yes.

03:01.360 --> 03:04.200
Marquis Wu'an's death
will cement my legend in Baxia.

03:04.800 --> 03:07.400
Brother, be sure to come
watch the battle then.

03:07.480 --> 03:10.040
Witness my siege
and the killing of Marquis Wu'an.

03:10.120 --> 03:12.520
Marquis Wu'an is hitting a rock
with an egg this time.

03:12.600 --> 03:14.160
No Yanzhou army in reserve.

03:14.240 --> 03:16.400
He only brought
a thousand Jizhou soldiers here.

03:17.000 --> 03:19.320
I can't help but feel somewhat uneasy.

03:21.800 --> 03:22.720
So what?

03:22.800 --> 03:26.400
The world considers him the reincarnation
of Great General Tian Ce.

03:26.960 --> 03:29.960
But this time, I have an army at my back.

03:30.720 --> 03:32.600
And we have that little girl as a hostage.

03:34.280 --> 03:35.440
Bring her up.

03:39.600 --> 03:41.640
Let go of me!

03:47.560 --> 03:48.440
Little girl.

03:49.160 --> 03:50.320
Don't let your asthma flare up, okay?

03:52.920 --> 03:54.920
Your father is coming to save you.

03:57.840 --> 03:58.960
From now on, in this world,

03:59.040 --> 04:00.840
there will only be the reputation
for you as the heir of Prince Changxin.

04:00.920 --> 04:02.360
No more "Little Marquis Wu'an".

05:31.720 --> 05:36.560
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:42.400 --> 05:43.360
Thank you.

05:46.160 --> 05:47.000
Hurry.

05:47.080 --> 05:48.000
Sit here.

05:52.320 --> 05:54.280
Why does that big fellow get a drumstick?

05:56.320 --> 05:58.640
I heard from that sergeant

05:59.440 --> 06:01.240
that he dragged a huge basket

06:01.320 --> 06:04.520
up the mountain all by himself
without using a cart.

06:05.960 --> 06:07.400
I see.

06:07.480 --> 06:08.920
If you want drumsticks,

06:09.000 --> 06:10.760
you need to work harder.

06:10.840 --> 06:12.480
What do you know?

06:12.560 --> 06:14.960
That basket weighs
over a hundred kilograms!

06:15.040 --> 06:16.800
You may pull it off,
but it'll cost your life.

06:17.760 --> 06:19.880
Old man, want a drumstick?

06:21.760 --> 06:24.320
I'm teaching you the knowledge
from Confucius and Mencius.

06:24.400 --> 06:28.160
Why are you only thinking
about that bit of carnal desire?

06:29.120 --> 06:30.360
I'm listening.

06:30.440 --> 06:36.520
"Demand much from oneself,
but little from others…

06:37.400 --> 06:38.560
keeps resentment at bay."

06:39.320 --> 06:42.560
That is to say, for everything, reflect
less on yourself, blame others more.

06:42.640 --> 06:43.920
See, he teaches it so well.

06:44.000 --> 06:45.640
Do you want the drumstick or not?

06:45.720 --> 06:47.000
Utterly vulgar.

06:49.440 --> 06:51.280
Got the strength to eat that meat?

06:51.360 --> 06:53.200
If you had even a fraction

06:53.280 --> 06:54.880
of that big fellow's strength,

06:54.960 --> 06:56.640
I'd twist my head off

06:56.720 --> 06:57.960
and let you use it as a soccer ball.

06:58.840 --> 07:00.400
Believe it or not, I'll twist
your head off right now

07:00.480 --> 07:01.840
-and use it as a ball!
-Come and try it!

07:01.920 --> 07:03.120
-What?
-What are you doing?

07:03.200 --> 07:04.760
-What? Try it!
-What's going on?

07:05.760 --> 07:06.680
Sit down and eat.

07:09.400 --> 07:10.280
Go eat our meals.

07:14.160 --> 07:16.440
Since that poker-faced officer came,

07:16.520 --> 07:18.440
they stopped rushing
on our quarrying progress.

07:18.520 --> 07:19.920
Seems like a good official.

07:24.800 --> 07:25.640
Be careful.

07:25.720 --> 07:26.880
-Must ensure every person--
-Officer!

07:28.520 --> 07:30.040
No news turned up yet.

07:30.120 --> 07:31.520
I'm not asking about that.

07:32.920 --> 07:35.440
If I carry those two big baskets of stone
up the mountain,

07:35.960 --> 07:38.320
can you get drumsticks for my friends?

07:38.400 --> 07:41.040
Lady, don't joke.

07:41.600 --> 07:42.960
Two big baskets

07:43.040 --> 07:45.360
usually takes
four big men straining to lift.

07:45.440 --> 07:46.880
You'll be lucky to even lift it.

07:47.760 --> 07:49.600
I know. But do you have drumsticks?

07:50.320 --> 07:52.880
Leave alone the drumsticks.
If you can do it,

07:53.400 --> 07:55.400
I'll reward each of you
with a whole chicken.

07:57.080 --> 07:58.320
She even dreams about more!

08:01.920 --> 08:02.760
Is she really?

08:29.480 --> 08:30.520
Oh my…

08:32.120 --> 08:33.120
Amazing!

08:33.200 --> 08:34.760
This girl is too powerful!

08:36.799 --> 08:38.880
-Go! Come on!
-Go, girl!

08:38.960 --> 08:40.280
-Well done!
-Fan's got it!

08:40.360 --> 08:41.200
Go for it!

08:41.280 --> 08:42.640
Truly divine strength!

08:42.720 --> 08:44.760
See? We're all on the same side.

08:46.760 --> 08:47.920
Look at it!

08:48.000 --> 08:49.800
Good thing we didn't act just now.

08:50.640 --> 08:53.120
If we'd really fought,
we'd have lost our lives.

08:53.200 --> 08:54.120
Amazing.

08:54.200 --> 08:55.040
Well done!

08:56.840 --> 08:57.840
Amazing!

08:57.920 --> 08:58.880
-Go!
-Incredible!

08:58.960 --> 09:00.920
-Off you go!
-Come on!

09:01.000 --> 09:01.920
-Impressive!
-Come on!

09:02.000 --> 09:04.440
There is actually such divine strength.

09:05.120 --> 09:06.720
A true heroine among women.

09:09.240 --> 09:10.760
-I can't even lift one basket.
-Incredible!

09:17.200 --> 09:18.080
Brother.

09:22.160 --> 09:23.520
-Thanks, Fan!
-Thank you!

09:23.600 --> 09:24.600
I'll help myself then.

09:24.680 --> 09:25.520
Let's eat.

09:28.760 --> 09:30.760
A young girl like you…

09:30.840 --> 09:33.400
Why can you have such great strength?

09:33.480 --> 09:35.040
My father taught me.

09:35.120 --> 09:37.320
Engage your core and legs.
Drive through the ground up.

09:37.920 --> 09:39.240
Your waist and legs act as one.

09:39.320 --> 09:40.680
Effortless and steady.

09:42.520 --> 09:44.520
Your father was truly a wise man.

09:44.600 --> 09:46.360
How was the route exploration?

09:50.640 --> 09:52.600
How did you know?

09:56.280 --> 09:59.400
When you went up the mountain,
your shoes were stained with yellow mud.

10:00.080 --> 10:02.760
When you returned,
they were stained with black mud.

10:04.760 --> 10:07.800
You probably sought out a forest path.

10:08.440 --> 10:09.400
I reckon

10:09.480 --> 10:12.200
you wanted nothing more
than to investigate

10:12.280 --> 10:15.320
the nearby terrain and military defenses.

10:17.080 --> 10:19.200
Rest assured, I won't sneak out

10:19.280 --> 10:20.720
and cause trouble for everyone.

10:20.800 --> 10:21.880
I just think

10:21.960 --> 10:23.840
the mountain stone we're quarrying
is too rough.

10:23.920 --> 10:25.360
Definitely not for paving roads.

10:25.440 --> 10:27.240
When I was captured and brought in,

10:27.320 --> 10:29.160
I noticed the river level
seemed unusually low.

10:29.240 --> 10:30.680
So I wanted to go up and check.

10:30.760 --> 10:33.400
But I got stopped by soldiers halfway.

10:33.480 --> 10:36.360
On the way back, I secretly
took a forest path up the mountain.

10:36.960 --> 10:38.760
And I saw it. It is true
they are building a dam.

10:44.360 --> 10:46.880
I just wanted to see
how the dam construction was going

10:46.960 --> 10:48.120
and know when we can leave.

10:49.520 --> 10:52.200
Do as you please. I don't care.

10:52.280 --> 10:53.760
I just want to ask you

10:54.560 --> 10:56.640
to do an urgent thing for me.

10:58.120 --> 10:59.320
What is it?

11:02.120 --> 11:04.440
Tomorrow at dusk,

11:04.520 --> 11:07.600
can you go up again to the mountain top?

11:20.320 --> 11:25.000
Nanny, when can you rescue my mother
and Ning?

11:26.480 --> 11:27.800
Don't worry, Bao'er.

11:28.320 --> 11:31.400
Your father won't harm your mother.

11:32.320 --> 11:34.800
This is also your mother's plan.

11:34.880 --> 11:37.240
When the time comes,

11:37.320 --> 11:39.120
you'll be able to meet.

11:45.720 --> 11:47.640
-Who's there?
-It's me.

11:48.240 --> 11:49.080
Master.

11:53.440 --> 11:54.280
Mother!

11:57.320 --> 11:58.200
Xun'er!

11:58.280 --> 11:59.880
Mother and Young Master had a hard time.

12:00.560 --> 12:01.560
It's good that you're alright.

12:02.160 --> 12:03.480
Come with Mother.

12:03.560 --> 12:06.080
I have to delay the Master,
so you can escape.

12:06.160 --> 12:08.560
You proceed first according to our plan.

12:09.120 --> 12:10.960
This is still within Baxia.

12:11.040 --> 12:12.400
You shouldn't stay long.

12:12.480 --> 12:14.520
You must take good care of yourself.

12:14.600 --> 12:16.320
Mother, don't worry.

12:16.400 --> 12:18.320
You take Bao'er and set off quickly.

12:18.400 --> 12:19.480
I'll come find you later.

12:38.680 --> 12:40.600
Where did that little brat
run off to? Tell me!

12:42.720 --> 12:44.040
Do you think I'll tell you?

12:44.640 --> 12:46.760
When did you collude with Nanny Lan?

12:46.840 --> 12:48.080
Speak up!

12:55.520 --> 12:57.680
From the day you stepped into the manor,

12:57.760 --> 12:59.680
you've been thinking of how to deceive me.

12:59.760 --> 13:01.360
This was all to get yourself free, right?

13:02.440 --> 13:03.800
You liar.

13:06.840 --> 13:08.080
So what if I am?

13:09.040 --> 13:11.360
Show me your guts
and stop playing the victim.

13:11.440 --> 13:13.200
You make it seem like everyone owes you.

13:13.880 --> 13:14.800
Disgusting.

13:16.640 --> 13:18.000
Just kill me.

13:20.840 --> 13:21.760
Fine.

13:26.760 --> 13:28.640
But I won't kill you.

13:29.360 --> 13:31.880
And you also can forget
about leaving my side.

13:36.320 --> 13:38.600
Guards, lock her in the firewood shed.

13:39.200 --> 13:40.480
From today onward,

13:40.560 --> 13:42.800
no one is allowed near that room.

13:43.480 --> 13:44.480
And also,

13:44.560 --> 13:46.280
find Zhao Xun for me.

13:46.360 --> 13:47.200
Yes.

13:52.760 --> 13:53.880
Speak!

13:53.960 --> 13:56.680
Where did Nanny Lan
and that little brat go?

13:56.760 --> 13:57.800
My lord.

13:57.880 --> 13:59.920
I've been in the army these past few days.

14:00.000 --> 14:02.320
All the officers and soldiers
can testify for me.

14:03.080 --> 14:07.080
The Zhao family has served you
for generations.

14:07.160 --> 14:08.480
Everyone can see it.

14:09.440 --> 14:11.760
This matter is truly strange.

14:11.840 --> 14:14.760
My mother and the Young Master

14:14.840 --> 14:17.000
must have been lured away by the enemy.

14:17.080 --> 14:20.480
It's the enemy's scheme, Master!

14:29.120 --> 14:33.520
PURE THOUGHTS

14:52.400 --> 14:54.200
M-m-my lord!

14:54.280 --> 14:56.440
An old woman and a child.
They can't have gone far.

14:57.040 --> 14:58.680
We still have time to chase them down.

14:58.760 --> 15:00.600
You can chase them back, my lord.

15:00.680 --> 15:01.960
Interrogate them clearly.

15:02.040 --> 15:04.080
You can kill me after that

15:04.840 --> 15:06.200
Alright.

15:07.360 --> 15:09.160
In consideration

15:09.840 --> 15:11.560
of your mother and son's long devotion,

15:12.400 --> 15:14.040
I'll trust you once.

15:15.760 --> 15:17.640
Send people to look immediately.

15:18.240 --> 15:19.560
Yes.

15:28.200 --> 15:31.520
My lord, this Zhao Xun
may not be trustworthy.

15:33.200 --> 15:34.720
Of course I know.

15:36.320 --> 15:38.320
Nothing but a trick to snare me.

15:42.320 --> 15:45.160
He will definitely meet
with that little brat.

16:04.880 --> 16:05.720
Madam.

16:09.800 --> 16:10.840
What are you doing here?

16:11.760 --> 16:12.600
Madam.

16:15.520 --> 16:17.240
I saw you haven't eaten for two days.

16:17.320 --> 16:18.400
I brought you some food.

16:31.640 --> 16:32.960
Did your lord send you?

16:34.520 --> 16:35.480
I stole it.

16:36.200 --> 16:37.480
This is all I could sneak
from the kitchen.

16:37.560 --> 16:38.960
Please make do with it.

16:39.040 --> 16:40.120
When I get my monthly wages tomorrow,

16:40.200 --> 16:41.920
I will buy you some meat buns.

16:49.080 --> 16:49.960
Right.

16:50.040 --> 16:51.280
If it was that lunatic,

16:52.480 --> 16:54.160
the dishes would certainly
be much more lavish.

17:18.440 --> 17:20.079
Why are you so good to me?

17:20.640 --> 17:23.760
I once served an old lady before.

17:23.839 --> 17:26.680
The master locked her in the firewood shed
and she starved to death.

17:27.400 --> 17:29.280
Madam, you mustn't die.

17:30.640 --> 17:32.880
Don't worry, I won't die.

17:32.960 --> 17:35.880
Don't come again with food.

17:35.960 --> 17:37.720
If they find out, you'll be in danger.

17:37.800 --> 17:39.880
Rest assured, madam, I won't.

17:43.040 --> 17:44.640
Eat slowly. I'll go back first.

18:07.280 --> 18:11.360
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

18:14.920 --> 18:15.760
Here.

18:17.040 --> 18:19.040
I've written down everything you asked.

18:19.120 --> 18:20.040
From south to north,

18:20.120 --> 18:21.640
here, here,

18:27.480 --> 18:28.720
and here.

18:28.800 --> 18:30.600
There are boreholes in these spots.

18:32.240 --> 18:34.240
These bastards.

18:36.600 --> 18:41.120
Of all places, they drilled holes
for the vents here.

18:45.480 --> 18:46.720
Stupid.

18:49.240 --> 18:51.000
Stupid indeed.

18:57.880 --> 19:00.440
Drilling vents here…

19:10.160 --> 19:11.080
Madness.

19:13.600 --> 19:14.680
Madness.

19:24.880 --> 19:26.120
There are soldiers outside!

19:26.200 --> 19:27.600
-Halt!
-Halt!

19:29.840 --> 19:31.440
Take me to see your general.

19:34.280 --> 19:35.240
What do we do?

19:38.920 --> 19:41.160
General, an old man insists on seeing you.

19:41.240 --> 19:42.400
-Bring him in.
-Yes.

19:49.680 --> 19:50.520
General.

19:51.040 --> 19:53.920
May I ask? Was it you
who ordered men to drill vents

19:54.000 --> 19:55.440
at the Qinglong position?

19:55.520 --> 19:58.400
Could it be to breach the dam
and release water?

20:00.400 --> 20:02.240
Who exactly are you?

20:05.000 --> 20:08.240
General, the spring flood hasn't arrived.
Water power is insufficient.

20:08.320 --> 20:10.240
If vents are made here,

20:10.840 --> 20:14.200
I'm afraid it will be hard
to achieve the scale you want.

20:15.960 --> 20:17.600
In my opinion,

20:18.200 --> 20:22.240
vents should be made
at the Qian, Xun, Gen, and Dui.

20:22.760 --> 20:24.280
These four positions.

20:24.960 --> 20:28.080
Only then can your goal be achieved.

20:29.400 --> 20:30.520
Quickly bring the chief engineer to me.

20:30.600 --> 20:31.600
Yes.

20:33.680 --> 20:34.520
Sir,

20:35.440 --> 20:36.320
may I ask your name?

20:36.400 --> 20:39.080
I am the former Minister of Works

20:39.160 --> 20:42.040
and the current Grand Tutor, Tao Yi.

20:43.200 --> 20:45.960
Grand Tutor Tao, why are you here?

20:46.040 --> 20:48.240
No need to ask, General.

20:48.320 --> 20:51.280
Just tell me. If you breach the dam
to release the flood,

20:51.360 --> 20:55.560
what about the soldiers
and laborers at the dam?

21:12.320 --> 21:13.440
Give me some water.

21:14.400 --> 21:15.440
Here.

21:22.760 --> 21:23.760
What are you laughing at?

21:24.440 --> 21:28.000
Madam, you're different
from the madams I served before.

21:31.960 --> 21:32.800
How so?

21:34.440 --> 21:35.800
Those madams before,

21:35.880 --> 21:37.200
if punished by the master,

21:37.280 --> 21:38.960
they would certainly lose their appetite.

21:39.040 --> 21:40.680
Just thinking of starving themselves thin,

21:40.760 --> 21:43.000
so the master would pity them
and lessen the punishment.

21:43.080 --> 21:45.440
Relying on others' pity to live…

21:49.120 --> 21:50.320
Listen to me.

21:50.400 --> 21:52.400
Better to rely on yourself
than on anyone else.

21:53.240 --> 21:54.840
I need to eat
to have the strength to escape.

22:01.440 --> 22:02.920
Madam, where did you get that knife?

22:04.160 --> 22:05.440
I found it in this firewood shed.

22:06.160 --> 22:07.240
But I sharpened it a bit.

22:08.040 --> 22:09.760
Madam, you mustn't contemplate suicide.

22:10.480 --> 22:13.280
Don't worry, I won't kill myself.

22:21.880 --> 22:22.720
Right.

22:23.280 --> 22:24.720
No matter what happens in the future,

22:24.800 --> 22:26.560
just run for yourself.
Don't worry about me.

22:33.000 --> 22:34.200
Did everything go alright last night?

22:35.360 --> 22:37.640
This chicken is for you.
They wanted it. I didn't agree.

22:40.080 --> 22:42.640
I'm fine. Thank you for your concern.

22:48.960 --> 22:51.800
Tao, tell me. Why must this dam

22:51.880 --> 22:54.440
be finished before
the next rainstorm arrives?

22:55.600 --> 22:58.280
After the storm, can we leave?

22:59.000 --> 23:00.200
What are "vents"?

23:03.480 --> 23:06.440
Firstly, you haven't given me tuition.

23:06.520 --> 23:08.480
Secondly, you haven't offered me tea

23:08.560 --> 23:10.480
and kowtowed to me,
acknowledging me as your teacher.

23:10.560 --> 23:13.600
You asked me too many questions.

23:13.680 --> 23:16.680
Why should I teach you?

23:18.760 --> 23:19.600
Alright.

23:21.320 --> 23:22.720
Are you still having this chicken?

23:24.160 --> 23:26.040
Silly pig slaughtering girl.

23:26.120 --> 23:27.920
That's all the wisdom you have.

23:29.960 --> 23:31.000
-Take it and share.
-See? What did I say?

23:31.080 --> 23:32.800
He won't eat it.
Of course, we will have it.

23:33.720 --> 23:34.640
Save me a drumstick.

23:38.160 --> 23:39.440
There's no tea here.

23:39.520 --> 23:44.080
Couldn't you offer porridge, kowtow,
and acknowledge me as your teacher?

23:48.520 --> 23:49.800
You want me to be your student?

23:53.680 --> 23:54.840
This weird old man.

23:54.920 --> 23:57.160
Looking for someone to be his student
and see him off in old age.

23:57.240 --> 23:58.720
Now he picked me.

23:59.560 --> 24:01.520
Forget it. My mother said

24:01.600 --> 24:03.960
I don't have the brain for studying,
so don't waste your effort.

24:04.480 --> 24:05.320
You…

24:05.920 --> 24:07.200
You really don't know

24:07.280 --> 24:09.240
how many people would pay a thousand,

24:09.320 --> 24:11.160
no, 10,000,

24:11.240 --> 24:13.480
for me to take them as a student,
and I refused them all?

24:13.560 --> 24:14.960
Ten thousand?

24:16.400 --> 24:18.240
-Being a teacher pays that well?
-You…

24:19.800 --> 24:20.880
Sir, I love learning.

24:20.960 --> 24:22.480
I… I'll be your student.

24:22.560 --> 24:24.520
-You love learning?
-Yes, I do.

24:24.600 --> 24:26.520
Well, I don't want to teach you.

24:27.800 --> 24:29.520
This annoying old man. I quit.

24:31.160 --> 24:32.000
Where is my drumstick?

24:36.400 --> 24:37.640
Don't move.

24:45.680 --> 24:47.200
-Is it here?
-Yes.

24:56.600 --> 24:57.640
Try it now.

25:00.800 --> 25:01.800
That's amazing.

25:02.760 --> 25:04.920
Still want to act tough?

25:05.640 --> 25:08.640
-This old man.
-No tough act, no drumsticks.

25:08.720 --> 25:10.080
I'm no good at studying.

25:10.160 --> 25:12.440
But if you ever want drumsticks,
I can manage that.

25:12.520 --> 25:15.440
As long as I'm here,
you'll have enough meals.

25:24.320 --> 25:25.480
What are you looking at?

25:30.960 --> 25:32.240
Take this.

25:32.880 --> 25:33.720
What is it?

25:35.800 --> 25:38.160
In the future, if I'm not around,

25:38.240 --> 25:39.720
you can reveal it then.

25:44.160 --> 25:46.560
So this is the famous bag of tricks?

25:48.840 --> 25:50.040
Why are you giving me this?

25:52.640 --> 25:54.080
Treading a starving tiger's path，

25:54.160 --> 25:56.720
as precarious as a stack of eggs.

25:58.480 --> 26:01.600
-What eggs?
-If you don't understand, don't ask.

26:03.800 --> 26:05.200
We all know.

26:05.280 --> 26:07.240
Once this battle starts,

26:07.320 --> 26:08.720
there will be countless dead and wounded.

26:10.640 --> 26:14.240
Take this clever method to annihilate
the enemy in one fell swoop.

26:15.120 --> 26:16.800
Even if there will be sacrifices,

26:17.560 --> 26:19.440
it's for the future.

26:20.160 --> 26:23.080
More people will be spared from war.

26:24.960 --> 26:28.080
I know this strategy
comes at a moral cost,

26:28.680 --> 26:29.720
but I have to do it.

26:31.480 --> 26:34.120
General, if you take my suggestion

26:34.200 --> 26:35.760
and make vents at these four places,

26:36.360 --> 26:38.880
half the soldiers
and laborers would survive.

26:38.960 --> 26:41.360
The other half can be saved.

26:41.440 --> 26:43.120
This is a benevolent
and righteous strategy.

26:43.200 --> 26:45.400
I hope the General will think again.

27:01.640 --> 27:04.400
Sir, no Confucian chats today?

27:04.480 --> 27:05.680
Yeah.

27:05.760 --> 27:07.640
Sir, if you don't scold us,

27:07.720 --> 27:09.880
we won't enjoy chewing that steamed bun.

27:12.360 --> 27:15.000
Vulgar brats, fooling around all day.

27:15.080 --> 27:17.280
I disdain to teach you a lesson.

27:17.800 --> 27:19.200
Now that's the right flavor, isn't it?

27:19.760 --> 27:20.600
Tasty.

27:23.560 --> 27:25.120
Everyone, assemble!

27:27.240 --> 27:28.360
Assemble! Assemble!

27:28.440 --> 27:30.000
‎HE

27:30.920 --> 27:32.600
Move faster! Faster!

27:34.920 --> 27:35.800
Everyone listen.

27:36.320 --> 27:38.120
The front is heavily engaged.

27:38.200 --> 27:40.240
We need to divert some people
as reinforcements.

27:40.320 --> 27:41.720
To leave or to stay

27:41.800 --> 27:43.080
will be decided by drawing lots.

27:43.600 --> 27:44.880
Those who draw "leave"

27:44.960 --> 27:47.360
will withdraw with the army today.

27:47.440 --> 27:48.560
Those who draw "stay"

27:48.640 --> 27:49.800
will continue to stay.

27:51.680 --> 27:52.880
Who wants to leave?

27:53.560 --> 27:55.120
-Brother.
-Is there any coming back?

27:55.200 --> 27:56.880
-Going to the battlefield is suicide.
-Exactly.

27:56.960 --> 27:58.000
Staying here, at least we have food.

27:58.080 --> 27:59.160
Exactly.

27:59.240 --> 28:01.080
-We mustn't draw a "leave"!
-Right.

28:04.920 --> 28:06.120
-Do it.
-Life and death are fated.

28:06.200 --> 28:07.040
You guys.

28:11.440 --> 28:12.920
They drew "stay".

28:14.320 --> 28:15.840
-Can I not draw?
-No.

28:15.920 --> 28:16.840
I got a "stay".

28:16.920 --> 28:18.960
Please, give me a "stay"!

28:19.040 --> 28:21.000
Please, "stay". Which one is "stay"?

28:21.080 --> 28:22.120
Mine is "stay"!

28:22.200 --> 28:24.080
I got a "stay"!

28:25.000 --> 28:26.000
STAY

28:26.080 --> 28:27.200
What are yours?

28:27.960 --> 28:29.080
No idea.

28:29.160 --> 28:30.000
-They all look the same.
-This is…

28:30.080 --> 28:32.480
Brother, is this character
"leave" or "stay"?

28:34.160 --> 28:35.000
It is a fart.

28:35.080 --> 28:36.080
Fart?

28:37.320 --> 28:38.800
I don't know this character either.

28:39.520 --> 28:41.200
But I know the character for "leave".

28:41.280 --> 28:42.960
This isn't "leave". This is "stay".

28:43.040 --> 28:44.120
-Is this "stay"?
-It is.

28:44.200 --> 28:45.440
-It is.
-We're staying!

28:45.520 --> 28:46.560
This is "stay"!

28:46.640 --> 28:48.080
We're staying!

28:48.160 --> 28:49.120
Looks like this.

28:49.200 --> 28:50.600
I am staying!

28:50.680 --> 28:52.880
Stay! Must be stay!

28:53.560 --> 28:55.400
-All three of us are staying.
-We're all staying.

28:55.480 --> 28:56.560
-Then it's fine.
-All staying.

28:56.640 --> 28:57.920
Sir, aren't you looking at it?

28:59.120 --> 28:59.960
I'll help you.

29:01.280 --> 29:02.120
Let me see.

29:03.760 --> 29:05.800
STAY, LEAVE

29:10.400 --> 29:11.280
Don't worry.

29:12.360 --> 29:14.680
The army has age limits for enlistment.

29:14.760 --> 29:16.160
They won't make you go to war.

29:17.200 --> 29:18.040
Fan.

29:18.800 --> 29:22.120
Can I exchange my "leave" for your "stay"?

29:22.920 --> 29:24.000
Sir.

29:24.080 --> 29:25.280
What do you mean?

29:25.840 --> 29:27.920
Sir, we treated you sincerely.

29:28.000 --> 29:29.000
How can you harm Mrs. Fan?

29:29.080 --> 29:31.360
-Exactly!
-I'm not harming her.

29:31.440 --> 29:34.000
With my age, can I still fight?

29:34.080 --> 29:34.920
I…

29:35.560 --> 29:37.080
I'm timid.

29:37.160 --> 29:40.800
I fear death. I want to enjoy
a few more years of peace.

29:41.400 --> 29:43.200
Girl, can you help me?

29:43.280 --> 29:44.640
How can you say that?

29:44.720 --> 29:47.120
You don't want to die,
so you send a young girl into battle.

29:47.200 --> 29:48.080
You've gone too far.

29:48.160 --> 29:51.280
I am half a teacher to her.

29:51.360 --> 29:54.000
Kid, you still acknowledge me
as your teacher, right?

29:54.080 --> 29:55.200
Forget about that now.

29:55.280 --> 29:56.920
-No, we don't.
-Didn't you want to exchange?

29:57.000 --> 29:58.400
Come, I'll exchange with you. You want it?

29:58.480 --> 29:59.480
Come, we'll do it for you.

29:59.560 --> 30:01.080
-Come. You want it?
-Take it!

30:01.160 --> 30:02.080
Don't be angry.

30:02.680 --> 30:04.360
-I think it's good.
-How is this good?

30:04.440 --> 30:06.880
First, after I go out,
I can look for Ning.

30:07.440 --> 30:09.280
Second, I have martial skills.

30:09.360 --> 30:10.400
Not afraid to go to the battlefield.

30:14.120 --> 30:15.600
I've decided you're my teacher.

30:15.680 --> 30:17.880
After I leave here and find my sister,
I'll definitely come back to see you.

30:20.240 --> 30:21.920
Good girl.

30:22.000 --> 30:23.160
Good student.

30:25.240 --> 30:27.480
Good. Very good.

30:28.240 --> 30:30.200
-You…
-What, you just exchanged with him?

30:30.280 --> 30:32.440
-Fan!
-I wasted my effort helping you…

30:32.520 --> 30:34.600
Old man, you took a student
just for this, right?

30:36.040 --> 30:36.880
You get back here!

30:42.120 --> 30:44.560
HE

30:56.880 --> 31:00.240
Grand Tutor, you risk your life
for hers. Is it worth it?

31:02.200 --> 31:05.720
The "leave" lots were definitely
specially arranged by you.

31:06.280 --> 31:08.080
I appreciate it.

31:09.080 --> 31:11.680
The dam-breach flooding plan

31:11.760 --> 31:13.880
must have come from that
unworthy student of mine.

31:14.880 --> 31:17.520
It will kill so many innocent lives.

31:18.920 --> 31:21.720
As his teacher, I cannot just walk away.

31:23.640 --> 31:24.480
On another note,

31:25.800 --> 31:27.200
before I die,

31:27.280 --> 31:29.000
I've taken a good student.

31:31.400 --> 31:33.080
Worth it.

31:33.160 --> 31:34.560
Silly girl.

31:39.560 --> 31:40.400
Brother.

31:43.240 --> 31:45.560
But as for you, General,

31:45.640 --> 31:46.960
once the dam breaches,

31:48.080 --> 31:50.000
in the future, whether alive or dead,

31:50.800 --> 31:53.360
you will definitely
be ruined and disgraced.

31:54.520 --> 31:55.680
Is it worth it?

31:57.640 --> 32:00.640
Our soldiers' duty is to defeat the enemy.

32:01.360 --> 32:03.200
As for merits, faults, right and wrong,

32:03.760 --> 32:06.040
let future generations be the judge.

32:11.200 --> 32:12.040
Hurry up!

32:13.200 --> 32:14.520
Keep up!

32:14.600 --> 32:15.640
Faster!

32:15.720 --> 32:16.680
Don't fall behind.

32:19.440 --> 32:20.280
Quick, quick!

32:21.920 --> 32:23.280
Those behind, keep up!

32:25.720 --> 32:26.720
Fan Changyu!

32:27.880 --> 32:28.800
Hurry!

32:28.880 --> 32:29.720
Fan Changyu!

32:29.800 --> 32:30.920
Keep up! Keep up!

32:32.680 --> 32:33.600
-Fan Changyu!
-Stay close!

32:35.600 --> 32:36.440
Fan Changyu!

32:37.640 --> 32:38.600
-Behind, faster!
-Fan Changyu!

32:38.680 --> 32:39.520
Fan!

32:41.280 --> 32:42.680
-Fan!
-Fan!

32:42.760 --> 32:44.760
-Mrs. Fan!
-Fan Changyu!

32:44.840 --> 32:45.960
Fan!

32:46.040 --> 32:47.880
-Mrs. Fan!
-Fan Changyu!

32:55.040 --> 32:55.880
Fan!

32:58.000 --> 32:59.040
What are you doing?

32:59.720 --> 33:00.760
Never seen people
cutting in line to go die.

33:01.360 --> 33:02.200
You…

33:03.360 --> 33:05.120
People from Lin'an aren't cowards.

33:05.200 --> 33:06.840
No reason for you to go alone.

33:06.920 --> 33:09.040
Our lots were all exchanged with others.

33:09.120 --> 33:11.240
Now the whole camp thinks we're crazy.

33:11.320 --> 33:13.200
From now on, we're family.

33:13.280 --> 33:14.120
We go together.

33:14.200 --> 33:16.200
Exactly. Go together.

33:24.440 --> 33:26.240
Rest here tonight.

33:27.040 --> 33:28.480
We'll hit the road again early tomorrow.

33:29.880 --> 33:31.360
Can't hold it. Bro, you go over there.

33:32.600 --> 33:33.440
Are you crazy?

33:34.480 --> 33:36.720
I'm crazy. I am truly crazy.

33:38.160 --> 33:39.680
My brother and I only have each other.

33:40.520 --> 33:43.760
Now he lets me live,
stays behind to go die himself.

33:44.680 --> 33:46.720
-How can I accept that?
-It‘s an order!

33:47.600 --> 33:49.080
Our General also stayed.

33:49.160 --> 33:51.120
That Grand Tutor also stayed.

33:51.800 --> 33:53.720
He also exchanged lots with that girl.

33:54.600 --> 33:57.000
Laowu, this is all fate.

33:57.680 --> 34:00.440
We soldiers have to obey orders.

34:02.960 --> 34:04.000
Big news.

34:04.680 --> 34:06.840
Breaking news. Just now,
when we were relieving ourselves，

34:06.920 --> 34:09.480
we overheard soldiers saying
that stay means to die.

34:09.560 --> 34:10.440
What do you mean?

34:10.520 --> 34:12.000
That is to say,

34:12.080 --> 34:14.760
the old man staying behind
is to wait for his death.

34:16.360 --> 34:17.800
My teacher exchanged lots for me.

34:26.920 --> 34:29.040
‎ESCAPE

34:29.639 --> 34:30.840
Escape?

34:34.040 --> 34:35.520
He was afraid I was illiterate.

34:38.280 --> 34:39.880
He even drew a peach.

34:43.440 --> 34:45.320
Never thought that old man,
despite his temper,

34:45.920 --> 34:47.280
is a good man.

35:14.000 --> 35:15.560
Help! Help…

35:27.240 --> 35:28.440
Come at me!

35:34.480 --> 35:35.360
Get him!

35:38.080 --> 35:39.080
Come!

35:39.680 --> 35:40.960
Girl.

35:41.040 --> 35:42.560
Why are you back?

35:44.280 --> 35:46.440
You exchanged the lot with me.
You want me to escape

35:46.520 --> 35:48.400
and live on, right?

35:50.080 --> 35:52.640
Didn't you want to lead
your own people home?

35:52.720 --> 35:54.960
I grant you that.

35:55.040 --> 35:56.720
Child, you came back…

35:58.040 --> 36:00.240
to save me?

36:01.840 --> 36:03.960
Sentimental compassion of a woman.

36:12.640 --> 36:15.160
I've lost too many loved ones.
I can't take it anymore.

36:15.920 --> 36:16.800
From today onward,

36:16.880 --> 36:18.840
all of you must live for me.

36:19.400 --> 36:20.520
Get up.

36:21.040 --> 36:22.440
-Come!
-Go!

36:23.440 --> 36:24.760
Let go of me!

36:24.840 --> 36:25.960
You all go!

36:26.640 --> 36:27.840
Leave quickly!

36:27.920 --> 36:29.000
Once dawn breaks,

36:29.080 --> 36:32.160
-this place will be littered with corpses.
-Why?

36:32.880 --> 36:34.320
Why will it be littered with corpses?

36:34.400 --> 36:36.600
We must breach the dam
to flood the enemy army.

36:36.680 --> 36:39.600
The two armies
are about to engage at Baxia.

36:39.680 --> 36:41.160
Breaching the dam to release water

36:41.240 --> 36:42.760
can drown the rival armies.

36:43.760 --> 36:45.240
But at this critical moment,

36:45.320 --> 36:47.680
it was detected by Chongzhou's vanguard.

36:48.200 --> 36:51.200
General Tang was caught off guard by them.

36:52.840 --> 36:53.840
What can we do?

36:54.960 --> 36:56.800
First, save General Tang.

37:05.320 --> 37:06.320
General.

37:07.720 --> 37:08.560
General Tang.

37:09.160 --> 37:11.280
General Tang, I've come.

37:12.000 --> 37:13.920
Three scouts escaped.

37:14.000 --> 37:16.200
Quick! Chase along the back mountain.

37:16.280 --> 37:18.160
Must not let them get the message out.

37:18.240 --> 37:19.160
Changyu.

37:19.240 --> 37:21.800
We absolutely can’t let the scouts
get the message out.

37:21.880 --> 37:24.320
Otherwise, Marquis Wu'an's plan
to lure the enemy

37:24.400 --> 37:25.600
will surely fail.

37:26.200 --> 37:28.080
Once Marquis Wu'an is defeated,

37:28.160 --> 37:30.520
we will lose Lucheng and Jizhou.

37:30.600 --> 37:32.520
The country will be in great chaos.

37:32.600 --> 37:35.120
I understand.
Three pigs broke out of the pen.

37:36.000 --> 37:37.240
We need to bring them back.

37:37.320 --> 37:38.280
-Go!
-Let's go!

37:38.360 --> 37:39.200
Go!

37:43.600 --> 37:45.440
This old man acts young and wild.

37:46.240 --> 37:49.560
If I live, the enemy fails.
If I die, I die breaching the dam.

38:00.040 --> 38:00.960
By my sense of smell,

38:02.040 --> 38:02.880
all the way west.

38:05.640 --> 38:06.960
Quick! Run up!

38:11.240 --> 38:14.440
-Your nose is really sharp.
-Manwu's family used to be hunters.

38:20.080 --> 38:21.640
Miss Fan, save me!

38:21.720 --> 38:22.880
I'm not a villain.

38:22.960 --> 38:24.520
I have a family to raise.

38:26.240 --> 38:28.440
-Fated foes meet on a narrow path.
-How so?

38:29.040 --> 38:30.040
He tricked me.

38:30.120 --> 38:32.480
Then I was mistaken as an enemy scout

38:32.560 --> 38:33.600
and taken to the quarry.

38:35.600 --> 38:38.640
These ones must be the scouts from Sui.

38:40.120 --> 38:41.320
We can't let them go.

38:51.080 --> 38:53.520
-You alright?
-Don't mind me. Go notify the Prince now.

38:58.440 --> 39:00.240
We are at the shaded side of the mountain.

39:00.320 --> 39:01.920
They can't see it from the camp.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.600
We split up.

39:03.680 --> 39:05.520
First to the top sends the signal.

39:05.600 --> 39:08.560
We cannot let the Prince and the main army
fall for the dam-breaching trap.

39:08.640 --> 39:10.080
Everyone, split up and act.

39:11.920 --> 39:14.240
I'll chase the one in front.
The rest are up to you.

39:14.320 --> 39:15.720
-Okay.
-Good.

39:21.280 --> 39:24.960
HE

39:37.280 --> 39:39.920
Rest in peace, General Tang.

39:53.760 --> 39:55.040
Where is Marquis Wu'an?

39:56.400 --> 39:57.640
Come out and die!

40:02.760 --> 40:03.600
Kid.

40:04.520 --> 40:06.480
If your father
doesn't have the guts to save you,

40:06.560 --> 40:09.240
you might as well stay
in our Prince Changxin's mansion.

40:09.880 --> 40:11.720
My little nephew quite likes you.

40:11.800 --> 40:14.280
Being his little maid isn't bad either.

40:31.800 --> 40:33.960
Charge!

40:39.280 --> 40:40.720
HE

40:55.800 --> 40:56.920
Charge!

41:05.320 --> 41:07.400
I thought your lordship

41:07.480 --> 41:08.600
was too noble to show up.

41:19.320 --> 41:21.320
Taking a young child onto the battlefield,

41:22.040 --> 41:24.800
Prince Sui truly has quite the nerve.

41:27.520 --> 41:30.480
Zheng, save me!

41:31.800 --> 41:32.600
What did you just call him?

41:32.680 --> 41:34.400
My brother-in-law won't let you off!

41:34.480 --> 41:36.480
So you're not his daughter at all.

41:39.120 --> 41:40.320
If you keep acting up,

41:40.400 --> 41:41.360
I'll throw you off this horse right now

41:41.440 --> 41:42.560
and let you be trampled to death.

41:45.400 --> 41:46.520
if that's the case,

41:47.120 --> 41:49.000
there is no need to keep this girl alive.

41:49.960 --> 41:51.840
Zheng, help!

41:58.480 --> 41:59.360
Xie Wu.

42:07.600 --> 42:09.640
Xie Wu, take Changning
and meet up with the strategist.

42:09.720 --> 42:10.720
Yes.

42:42.360 --> 42:43.480
Your Highness.

42:44.120 --> 42:45.480
Another defeat.

42:49.720 --> 42:50.880
Report!

42:53.160 --> 42:54.280
Report! The Prince has been captured.

42:55.920 --> 42:58.080
My lord, what do we do?

42:58.160 --> 42:59.960
That's our troops of Chongzhou.

43:01.560 --> 43:04.720
The troops are only loyal to Sui Yuanqing.

43:04.800 --> 43:05.960
Their deaths are no loss.

43:07.240 --> 43:09.800
Shi Yue and the others
will arrive soon too with troops.

43:11.360 --> 43:13.560
It's just that Xie Zheng
only brought a thousand men.

43:14.200 --> 43:16.240
How can he deal with Sui Yuanqing?

43:17.960 --> 43:18.840
Rescue the Prince.

43:19.680 --> 43:21.440
-Attack!
-Attack!

43:21.520 --> 43:23.160
Attack!

43:23.240 --> 43:24.960
All troops, quickly head to Yixian Gorge.

43:33.440 --> 43:34.920
HE

43:47.440 --> 43:50.080
YIXIAN GORGE

44:03.280 --> 44:05.720
-It's you.
-It's me.

44:07.880 --> 44:10.200
Lady, spare me! I'm just a small soldier.

44:10.280 --> 44:12.400
Before, I was just following orders.
I don't know anything.

44:15.720 --> 44:17.560
I struck your vital point.

44:18.160 --> 44:19.480
Yet you ride and endure for so long.

44:20.520 --> 44:22.240
I am truly impressed.

44:24.200 --> 44:26.360
Is your spear made of wax?

44:27.440 --> 44:28.600
Next time, remember to use iron.

44:29.440 --> 44:32.080
You have barely over a thousand men
and no reinforcements.

44:33.040 --> 44:35.320
My soldiers will chase you
to the ends of the earth,

44:36.040 --> 44:37.560
until we witness your death.

44:40.000 --> 44:42.360
